The key words were not lacking in the letter from the WestLB steering committee to the employees of the house.
By a union of the entities of the Düsseldorf Financial Institute with the Frankfurt Deka-Bank, "the central financial market institution of the Sparkasse Financial Group" could be established, according to the letter published on Monday.
