However, the critical observers find, alongside all this, contradictions with worrying effects: for example, the company's top management has refused, in its entirety, the employees' protests, after it has doubled the price of the business kindergarten and after the company has considered the daily multiple restoration too expensive, taken at any time. All this seems to be derisory alongside the fact that already in 2006, Google has acquiesced before the Chinese government and according to the terms of their agreement, the company detects all the results that hurt the good taste, as well as the interests of the Chinese regime.
