On behalf of the European Year for Equal Opportunities for All, the objective of the Summit on Equal Opportunities in Europe, held every year since the Berlin Summit last year, is to ensure a single platform to support the measures taken to promote equal opportunities and to combat discrimination, aimed at the European level and at the level of the Member States.
