After nearly a year of work by voluntary developers, supervised by SUN Microsystem, the new Open Office package is shown to the general public with various new features: from the welcome screen, and the interface reviewed and become less austere, to more important ones, such as the compatibility born for the Apple Mac OS X operating system, and the support for the new ODF format (Open Document Format) 1.2, the latest standard ISO version.
